  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents a collection of binding parameters that store information used by binding elements to build factories.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection> is a collection of objects that is used when a custom binding needs to provide additional parameters to another binding. For example, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement> looks for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection> to determine Security auditing settings.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
